name: Ebay New Design Concept
description:
Hi everyone👋, I hope you all doing well.

Check out my redesign concept of the eBay website🔥

I tried to redesign what eBay could look like without the overloading information

that you come across on some of the detailed product pages.

If you want to show some love, press Like👍❤️.

You can write a comment with your opinion too📝.

--------------------------------

Have a nice day! 🍹☀️
